description: The VanEck European Equal Weight Screened UCITS ETF invests in 100 of the most liquid, highly capitalised (free float) companies from European industrialised nations that comply with the UN Global Compact Principles for responsible corporate behavior. Additionally, it excludes sectors that do not follow responsible business practices, including: alcohol, animal testing, military, weapons, gambling, pornography, tobacco, nuclear power, oil sands and thermal coat mining.
name: VanEck European Equal Weight Screened UCITS ETF
